      "rationale": "A continuum FEA formulation with frictional Coulomb contact (mu=0.2) and bilinear elastic-plastic material response for titanium alloy components was selected based on published ASTM F1717 modeling literature. The model form is consistent with the physics of quasi-static bending and is confirmed adequate by the validation comparison outcomes."
