      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested across two independent laboratories (n=6 Lab 1, n=5 Lab 2). All constructs were traceable to a single production lot. CMM dimensional inspection of three representative constructs confirmed geometry within drawing tolerance, supporting representative sampling at Gradation 3."
