      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison was performed for three QoIs (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) using both percent difference and the validation metric E/uval per ASME V&V 40. Pre-specified acceptance bounds (<10% difference, E/uval < 1.96) were met for all three QoIs across all eleven constructs, supporting Gradation 3."
